# In-app docs viewer staging directory. Populated by:
#   - docker compose dev: bind mount (`./docs:/app/_docs:ro` in docker-compose.yml)
#   - Render build: `cp -r ../docs ./_docs` in render.yaml buildCommand
# Never commit a snapshot — `docs/` at the repo root is the source of truth.
